Title: An Act Changing the Name of Tigloc Elementary School in the Municipality of Tungawan, Province of Zamboanga Del Sur, to Lower Tungawan Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 216
An Act Changing the Name of Tigloc Elementary School in the Municipality of Tungawan, Province of Zamboanga Del Sur, to Lower Tungawan Elementary School
Section 1. The name of Tigloc Elementary School in the Municipality of Tungawan, Province of Zamboanga del Sur, is hereby changed to Lower Tungawan Elementary School.1Ã¢wphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 25, 1982
